title: Angel and Faith 23 (Tablet Edition)
description:
This is from the original scanner. I adjusted the resolution and compressed the file for easier reading on tablets and ereaders. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.
  


Angel and Faith 23

By:   	Christos Gage, Rebekah Isaacs, Dan Jackson, Steve Morris	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Action-Adventure, Horror
Series:   	Angel
Publisher:   	Dark Horse	
Pub. Date:  	June 26, 2013
Format:         CBZ

Preventing Pearl, Nash, and Whistler from releasing their magical virus proves difficult for Angel and Faith. The duo is outmatched! Enter Nadira-could this hate-filled Slayer lend a helpful hand or will she use this opportunity to end Angel for good?

Showdown with this season's Big Bads!

"Joss Whedon fans, you need this comic."-Comic Book Resources
